PublicRemarks: LOOKING FOR GREAT TENANTS AS OF MAY 1.  Rent this new lower level 2 bedroom apartment close to parks, schools, transit, LRT station, St. Laurent Mall, lots of shopping and great eateries...and only 8 minutes to downtown! Recently completed, this rental boasts porcelain floors throughout (with radiant in-floor heating), almost 10 foot ceilings, large windows, in-unit laundry, gorgeous kitchen with gas range, quartz counters, breakfast bar, lots of cabinets and ample counter space, a bright living room with ceiling fan and a 4 piece bathroom. Rental comes with 1 parking spot and access to backyard patio. IDEAL RENTAL for young professionals, mature students or down-sizers. Credit Report, Rental Application and 2 recent pay stubs will be required to apply. Refrigerator, Gas Stove, Dishwasher, Hood Fan, Washer, Dryer all included. Rent is $1800/M + utilities, which on average will be about $90-$110/month. This apartment is bright and ready to move in! INTERIOR PHOTOS ARE OF A SIMILAR UNIT. (27840856)

PublicRemarks: Beautiful 2021 built energy-efficient coach house located in the rear yard in the heart of The Glebe! Located on a quiet street, this spacious 'smart house' has an option for up to 2 bedroom but has 2 bathroom *1 partial with high-quality finishes, a beautiful choice of materials & extra soundproofing. Solar-powered & plenty of natural light. It features a private fully finished side yard patio space with a gazebo. Includes also a communal patio furniture & BBQ area at the entrance. Pet friendly & walking distance from schools, parks, shopping & transportation. Utilities fixed fee 150$ per month (Hydro, Water, Gas) and enjoy a cozy ultra-private unit with no residential rear-neighbours! Parking available for 1 space in tandem if it fits (with other coach house) on right side driveway. Additional 125$ per month. (27919722)

PublicRemarks: Beautiful, Clean 2 bedroom upper level Spacious End-Unit stacked townhome conveniently located in the heart of Barrhaven with perfect orientation for quiet enjoyment and natural light. Open concept main living area and lots of windows for natural light all day. Large gourmet kitchen features stainless steel appliances, tiled backsplash, plenty of cabinets & counter space & large island with breakfast bar. Sliding patio door leads to large balcony. Upper level has very large primary bedroom with oversized closets, 2nd bedroom, full bath, along with convenient In-Unit laundry. 1 convenient parking spot & plenty of visitor parking. Great location across from a school and steps to parks & Nature Trails. A very short walk to Marketplace Mall which includes many stores & restaurants, including Loblaws, Walmart, Cineplex Theatres & the OC Transpo Marketplace Station. Close to Parks, trails and multiple schools. (27915056)

PublicRemarks: This spacious semi-detached three bedroom unit located along one of Carleton Place's main roads offers the perfect space for families just steps from shopping, restaurants, schools, and recreation. Step through the covered porch into the main floor, where a generously sized kitchen, living room, dining room, and back sitting room await someone who loves entertaining. The second floor features three bedrooms, a full bathroom, and an enclosed balcony towards the front of the property. The loft space on the third floor is perfect for storage! Tenant will be responsible for paying all utilities (including heat, hydro, and hot water tank rental) with the exception of water/sewer. (27769314)

PublicRemarks: Location is everything with this bright and spacious two bedroom unit.  Just a short walk from the Civic Campus of the Ottawa Hospital it would be a perfect spot for a health care professional.  It also has easy access to Highway 417, the Experimental farm and the great shops and restaurants of Wellington Village and Hintonburg.  Light pours in to the second floor unit where the hardwood floors gleam and the walls have a fresh coat of paint.  There is enough space to spread out here with two good sized bedrooms that are separate from the living and dining rooms and a great kitchen with a dishwasher and lots of room to make a gourmet meal.  Bonus space can be found on the deck off one of the bedrooms and in the three season sunroom off the living room.  Shared, coin laundry in the basement and parking for one car is also available.  No smoking please. (27957454)

PublicRemarks: Date Available: APR 1. UPPER LEVEL, END UNIT terrace urban home in Carson Meadows. Open-concept layout featuring modern finishes, hardwood floors, new pot lights and modern light fixtures throughout. Main level features a spacious living room, formal dining room and large windows for plenty of natural light. Kitchen offers walk in pantry, breakfast area, ceramic floors and patio doors leading to a south facing balcony. Upper floor has 2 generous-sized bedrooms both with private ensuite baths. Large balcony in the primary bedroom. Convenient laundry room are also on this level One outdoor parking space is included and plenty of visitor parking are also available. Walking distance to all necessary amenities, public transit, CMHC, Le Citie College and Monfort Hospital. Close to Montreal Road and Aviation Parkway. Easy access to walking and cycling paths. Please include proof of income, credit report & photo ID with rental application. No Pets, No Smokers, No roommates. (27912590)

Hurry up and call to book a showing! (27953706)

PublicRemarks: Bring your clothes and move in! A very clean and charming pied a terre in the heart of Ottawa. Central location within 3km of the Byward Market, Parliament Hill and all the other tourist attractions the city has to offer. This 2 Bedroom unit has extensive upgrades to bathroom and kitchen, new appliances washer/dryer, dishwasher. Fully furnished, including all utilities Gas, Hydro, Water and internet. Master bedroom includes a large closet, a queen size bed, and a beautiful quiet walk out balcony. The second bedroom is also furnished with a queen size bed and large closet. The kitchen is full stocked with dishes, pots and small appliances making it the perfect home away from home.  **Private entry, Parking in driveway.** (27931658)

PublicRemarks: Newly Built!! Be the first one to live in this brand new stacked townhouse located in the heart of Barrhaven. This beautiful and spacious house features 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and an upgraded kitchen with SS appliances and quartz Countertops. The quaint front porch and foyer lead upstairs into the living room/dining room. Step into the open concept kitchen and enjoy a cup of coffee or a meal at the charming breakfast bar. The living/dining space features patio doors that provide ample natural light, leading onto the balcony to enjoy the beautiful summer weather. Upstairs, escape to the privacy of the primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and master ensuite with a standing shower. Bedroom 2 has been upgraded to include its own private bath and has a private deck, providing amazing views of the surrounding community. Steps away from Barrhaven Marketplace, Parks, Public Transportation, Bus Stops, Schools, Shopping Malls, Grocery Stores, Restaurants, Bars and Sport Clubs. (27939812)

PublicRemarks: Date Available: APR 1. UPPER LEVEL, END UNIT terrace urban home in Carson Meadows. Open-concept layout featuring modern finishes, hardwood floors, new pot lights and modern light fixtures throughout. Main level features a spacious living room, formal dining room and large windows for plenty of natural light. Kitchen offers walk in pantry, breakfast area, ceramic floors and patio doors leading to a south facing balcony. Upper floor has 2 generous-sized bedrooms both with private ensuite baths. Large balcony in the primary bedroom. Convenient laundry room are also on this level One outdoor parking space is included and plenty of visitor parking are also available. Walking distance to all necessary amenities, public transit, CMHC, Le Citie College and Monfort Hospital. Close to Montreal Road and Aviation Parkway. Easy access to walking and cycling paths. Please include proof of income, credit report & photo ID with rental application. No Pets, No Smokers, No roommates. (27912590)

PublicRemarks: Lovely 2-bed, 3-bath upper end unit townhome for rent. Large, sun filled unit awaiting the perfect tenant. Enjoy the view on the 2 balconies. PublicRemarks: **BRAND NEW- Appliances included** Looking for an affordable bachelor to call home? Welcome to B-130 Carllion, a freshly constructed apartment showcasing top-tier designer finishes and impeccable craftsmanship. Nestled just a few steps from the Rideau River walking and biking trails, as well as proximity to all shopping, amenities, the University of Ottawa, major transit, and downtown, this residence offers an ideal location! The unit features an open-concept living and dining area that transitions to the bed space which includes built in storage. A designer kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, a stove, sleek push-to-open cabinets, quartz countertops, and ample counter and storage space. Affordable street parking permits are available. Tenants are responsible for hydro and gas expenses. (27785683)

PublicRemarks: **BRAND NEW - Appliances included** Introducing 138-B Carillon St., a freshly constructed lower-level 1-bedroom apartment showcasing top-tier designer finishes and impeccable craftsmanship. PublicRemarks: OCCUPANCY June 1st, 2024. Modern bachelor suite on top level with in-unit storage is nestled in the heart of Ottawa. This exquisite living space has been thoughtfully designed to provide luxury, comfort, and convenience to its residents. Step into this stylish unit & enjoy a blend of contemporary design & finishes. The rooftop terrace offers a tranquil oasis amidst the urban hustle, complete w/ seating & mesmerizing city views. The prime location ensures conveniences of downtown Ottawa. A plethora of trendy restaurants & entertainment venues & Convenient access to public transportation and major highways. (27891504)

PublicRemarks: Welcome to WE2, a luxury oasis in the heart of Gatineau. This 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo, with 675 square feet, offers a west-facing view of the common areas and the pool. Located on the 3rd floor, however the balcony overlooks the ground floor at the back. Available immediately, this unit invites you to enjoy exceptional amenities: rooftop pool, shared lounge, workspace, exercise room, yoga studio, indoor parking (+$), individual electric charging stations on demand (+$), grocery store on the ground floor (+$), pharmacy (+$), bistro resto. Discover the refinement of WE2 now. (38927490)

PublicRemarks: Date Available: MAY 1, Discover downtown living at its finest, this condo is Located in the heart of Centre Town. Walk score of 92! This location is a Walker’s Paradise so daily errands do not require a car. This unit comes with 1 Bed, 1 Full Baths and a nice balcony. Open-concept floor plan offers large windows and sliding door, in-unit laundry, hardwood floors throughout and a contemporary design. Kitchen boasts an island, granite counters, SS appliances and wood cabinets. Great room flooded with natural light and also comes with a cozy balcony. This condo offers a large rooftop deck for BBQ gathering, entertainment, and breathtaking city views. Don’t forget, only steps away from entertainment and shopping. Close to 417, Rideau Centre, University of Ottawa, LRT, Byward Market and Parliament. Please include proof of income, credit report & photo ID with rental application. No Pets, No Smokers, No roommates. (27961567)

PublicRemarks: Ottawa, Hintonburg! Lower level apartment of a triplex for rent. FULLY FURNISHED WITH HEAT AND WATER INCLUDED! Unit features 2 bedrooms and one 4pce bathroom. Bedrooms of good size. Vinyl plank flooring throughout. Bright living/dining area. Kitchen features ample counter space and white appliances. Washer and dryer (pay per use) located right beside unit. No carpets! Portable A/C. Close to Tunney's Pasture, Civic Hospital, Ottawa River, Wellington shops, restaurants and Parkdale Market. Easy bus to downtown and LRT. (27854574)

PublicRemarks: Settle into this inviting, airy, and recently updated 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom lower level apartment conveniently situated just steps away from Beechwood Village.
